@startuml
actor Client

participant "Mobile Application" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
participant "Payment Gateway" as Payment
participant "Coach" as Coach

Client -> App : Select paid plan
App -> API : Request plan purchase (planId)
API -> API : Validate user & plan availability
API -> Payment : Initiate payment
Payment -> Client : Payment confirmation UI
Client -> Payment : Confirm payment
Payment --> API : Payment success notification
API -> API : Register payment & activate plan
API -> Coach : Notify new client subscription
API --> App : Purchase success
App --> Client : Access to paid plan granted

@enduml
